        The information on this Website is provided for general informational purposes only. It does not constitute legal advice and should not be relied upon as such. You should not take or refrain from taking any action based solely on Website content. Always seek professional legal advice for your specific situation. Past results, articles, case studies, or other materials on this Website do not guarantee similar outcomes in future matters.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">No Firm-Client Relationship</h3>
