        Accessing or using this Website, or communicating with Firm personnel through email or online forms, does not create a firm-client, advisory, fiduciary, or other professional relationship. A firm-client relationship will be created only if we expressly agree to act on your behalf. Until such agreement is made, do not send us any confidential information.
      </p>

