      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">Link Agreement & Conditions</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Linking to this Website is prohibited unless we provide prior written authorization. We are not responsible for any content on your website. We may revoke your right to link to this Website at any time, and upon notice, you agree to remove all links immediately. By linking to this Website, you are deemed to accept these conditions.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">Links to Third-Party Sites</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        This Website may include links to third-party websites for your convenience. Such links do not constitute endorsements. We are not responsible for third-party content and make no representations or warranties.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">Disclaimer of Warranties</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Use of this Website and its Content is at your own risk. The Website and all Content are provided "as is" and "as available" without any warranties, representations, or conditions of any kind, whether express or implied. We are not responsible for changes made to Content by third parties.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, the Firm and its partners, employees, consultants, representatives, directors, agents, vendors, and licensors shall not be liable for any damages whatsoever including direct, indirect, incidental, special, punitive, or consequential damages arising from or related to use of the Website or third-party links.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">Entire Agreement & Governing Law</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        These Terms constitute the entire agreement between you and the Firm regarding your use of this Website and supersede all prior agreements related to the Website. This agreement is governed by the laws of the Province of Ontario.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Footer />
